Six persons have died in road crashes in Ogun and Ondo states. Three persons, one of whom an expectant mother, died in the Ogun crash which took place on Lagos-Ibadan Expressway. Four vehicles were involved in the accident. Three persons also died in the Ondo crash which took place yesterday on Oba Ile Road in Akure North council area. The accident involved a Toyota Corolla car and a Mercedes Benz bullion van.